  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db8\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel prices down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ceylon Petroleum Statutory Corporation took steps to reduce fuel prices from 10.00 tonight.",
        "Accordingly, a liter of octane 92 petrol and auto diesel have been reduced by 20 rupees, a liter of octane 95 petrol and a liter of super diesel have been reduced by 10 rupees.",
        "This price drop has been made according to the last two weeks adjustments in the fuel price formula."
      ],
